# Python

- **pixi project:** `pixi install`, `pixi run вА¶`, `pixi add вА¶` вАФ lock versions in `pixi.lock`.
- **uv project:** `uv sync`, `uv run вА¶`, `uv add вА¶` вАФ lock versions in `uv.lock`.
- Do not use bare `python` or ad-hoc `pip install` into `$HOME` when a project manager exists.
- **Platform CLIs** (`canfar`, `cadcdata`, `astroai-lab`): image venv at `/opt/astroai/venv/cadc`; in-session bump via `upgrade-cadc-tools.sh`, not project pixi/uv.
- Docs: Context7 MCP or official pixi/uv docs вАФ not invented wrapper commands.
- Type hints on public functions; run project linters when present.
- Jupyter: `astroai-lab kernel register` after env resume when paths change.
